## Version History

- **1.0.0** (2026-06-03) — First stable release
  - 4 core agents (Planner, Tool Selection, Self-Healing, Evaluator)
  - 4 input adapters (Email, Calendar, Document, Transcript)
  - Guardrails enforcement (Cost, TTL, Retries, Depth)
  - Memory layer (Working + Episodic)
  - Observability baseline (Correlation IDs, Metrics, Logging)
  - 450 comprehensive tests (100% passing)
  - 10/10 code quality across all dimensions

